<body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" tts:textAlign="center">
    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:30.566" end="00:00:34.547">&#65279;&#9834; [Music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:47.094" end="00:00:50.333" region="top"> Year 6 of the AIDS epidemic. </p>
      <p begin="00:00:54.729" end="00:00:59.496" region="top"> Greenwich Village, New York City.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>The epicenter. $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:07.024" end="00:01:12.496" region="top"> With no drugs to treat the disease,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>AIDS is nearly 100% fatal. $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:12.496" end="00:01:16.369" region="top"> Panic drives a backlash<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>of blame and anti-gay violence. </p>
      <p begin="00:01:16.369" end="00:01:19.243" region="top"> Even hospitals<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>routinely turn away the dying. $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:26.040" end="00:01:28.702" region="top"> Fighting for their lives,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>patients and their advocates $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:28.702" end="00:01:30.902" region="top"> take matters into their own hands. </p>
      <p begin="00:01:31.535" end="00:01:34.312">- Welcome to ACT UP. We are <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>the AIDS Coalition</p>
      <p begin="00:01:34.312" end="00:01:36.541">- [together] to unleash power.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:36.541" end="00:01:39.951">A diverse, non-partisan group<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and individuals united in anger</p>
      <p begin="00:01:39.951" end="00:01:42.002">and committed to direct action</p>
      <p begin="00:01:42.002" end="00:01:44.025">-[together] to end the AIDS crisis.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:44.025" end="00:01:51.562">- In less than 12 hours from now,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>we are gonna be taking over City Hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:51.854" end="00:01:54.008">[Applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:01:54.008" end="00:01:55.727">[Crowd chanting]</p>
      <p begin="00:01:55.727" end="00:01:57.992">- [Ed Koch] Yes.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>- [male reporter] Mr. Mayor,</p>
      <p begin="00:01:57.992" end="00:01:59.160">in campaigning <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>for the lesbian and gay vote,</p>
      <p begin="00:01:59.160" end="00:02:01.961">in an election year, a bit of<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>historical context is necessary</p>
      <p begin="00:02:01.961" end="00:02:04.059">in dealing with the AIDS crisis<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in New York City.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:04.059" end="00:02:06.111">It wasn't until 1983 that you met</p>
      <p begin="00:02:06.111" end="00:02:08.177">with people to deal with<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>the AIDS crisis.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:08.177" end="00:02:09.383">How do you respond to these questions?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:09.383" end="00:02:10.559">- [Ed] That it's a falsehood.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:10.559" end="00:02:13.312">- Please, anybody who's<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>thinking about being arrested,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:13.312" end="00:02:17.844">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">fill out a support sheet, make sure<br/>your support person knows who you are</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:17.889" end="00:02:20.094">and what group you're in.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>Yeah?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:20.263" end="00:02:25.748">- Um, if we end up in The Tombs,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>is there like a queer tank there</p>
      <p begin="00:02:25.748" end="00:02:28.748">and would you recommend that we<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>ask to be there?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:28.748" end="00:02:31.332">- There is a homo tank<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and I've been there</p>
      <p begin="00:02:31.332" end="00:02:33.680">and it's better than the straight tank,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>let me tell you.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:33.680" end="00:02:34.845">- [Ed] Who else? Yes?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:34.845" end="00:02:38.504">- [reporter] In the past,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>you've described ACT UP as fascist</p>
      <p begin="00:02:38.504" end="00:02:40.575">yet in the press release, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>you called them concerned citizen.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:40.575" end="00:02:43.051">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was wondering <br/>what changed your mind?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:43.051" end="00:02:45.649">- [Ed] I don't think <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that you can't use both.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:45.649" end="00:02:48.402">Fascist can be concerned citizens.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:49.539" end="00:02:55.706">And I don't believe they are fascist.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I think they have used the fascist tactic.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:55.706" end="00:03:00.155">- Let us celebrate together<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>tonight, the end of the last day</p>
      <p begin="00:03:00.155" end="00:03:02.463">on which Ed Koch can tell himself</p>
      <p begin="00:03:02.463" end="00:03:06.097">that the communities which are <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>being decimated by this epidemic</p>
      <p begin="00:03:06.097" end="00:03:09.331">are so weak and so divided <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>among themselves</p>
      <p begin="00:03:09.331" end="00:03:12.012">that he can keep serving us<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>this kind of bullshit.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:12.012" end="00:03:12.786">[laughter]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:12.848" end="00:03:15.527">Tomorrow morning, he will begin<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to learn the truth.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:15.527" end="00:03:17.217">[applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:18.131" end="00:03:21.687">- [Female voice] ACT UP, stand tall<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>tomorrow morning at city hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:21.687" end="00:03:25.640">- [Crowd] ACT UP, stand tall<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>tomorrow morning at city hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:25.640" end="00:03:29.482">ACT UP, stand tall,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>tomorrow morning at city hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:29.482" end="00:03:31.303">ACT UP, stand tall...</p>
      <p begin="00:03:31.303" end="00:03:34.917">&#9834; [Music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:03:39.508" end="00:03:41.562" region="top"> City Hall </p>
      <p begin="00:04:02.932" end="00:04:05.814">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [male reporter] We're talking <br/>to Jim Eigo</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:05.814" end="00:04:08.911">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">for the Treatment Issues Committee<br/>of ACT UP.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:08.911" end="00:04:10.269">Jim, what specific treatment issues</p>
      <p begin="00:04:10.269" end="00:04:12.766">are pretty important <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in this demonstration this week?</p>
      <p begin="00:04:12.766" end="00:04:16.133">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Jim Eigo] The municipal hospitals<br/>are totally falling apart.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:16.133" end="00:04:19.049">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">More than half the people<br/>who get diagnosed with AIDS today</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:19.049" end="00:04:22.428">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">get diagnosed in the emergency rooms<br/>of our city.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:22.428" end="00:04:24.561">You're going to find yourself <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>waiting four days</p>
      <p begin="00:04:24.561" end="00:04:27.408">in an emergency room before<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>you get a bed.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:27.678" end="00:04:31.664">- I'm pretty scared about being <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>HIV positive.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:31.718" end="00:04:33.304">I don't have much choice in the matter.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:33.304" end="00:04:34.526">- I just love all these people</p>
      <p begin="00:04:34.526" end="00:04:37.250">and I think that what we're <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>doing is really right.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:37.250" end="00:04:40.554">And -- I mean, listen to this <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and look at our people,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40.554" end="00:04:42.204">it's just really wonderful</p>
      <p begin="00:04:42.204" end="00:04:44.078">and it's worth putting<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/><span tts:fontStyle="italic">ourselves on the line. </span></p>
      <p begin="00:04:44.078" end="00:04:46.289">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Ann Northrop] There is<br/>no accurate diagnosis.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:04:46.289" end="00:04:48.248">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There are incentives<br/>in the city hospitals</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:48.248" end="00:04:50.269">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">not to diagnose people with AIDS,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:50.269" end="00:04:52.852">and therefore people don't get treated.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:52.852" end="00:04:56.259">We are angry at the way this city<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>has handled this crisis</p>
      <p begin="00:04:56.259" end="00:04:59.837">and we demand that Ed Koch<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>exert leadership</p>
      <p begin="00:04:59.837" end="00:05:02.417">and declare a state of emergency.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:02.440" end="00:05:03.823">[Applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:05:03.823" end="00:05:07.052">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Peter] Go on the street now or wait,<br/>those are the options.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:07.052" end="00:05:08.678">One. He says go.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:08.678" end="00:05:09.687">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-Two, now.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:09.687" end="00:05:10.845">-He says now, three.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:11.122" end="00:05:11.920">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Don?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:12.136" end="00:05:13.164">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Go now--</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:13.164" end="00:05:14.923">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[Reporter] I'm standing here<br/>with Larry Kramer</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:14.977" end="00:05:17.354">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What is ACT UP trying to say today<br/>to Ed Koch?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:17.354" end="00:05:19.570">-We're sending a message<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to public officials,</p>
      <p begin="00:05:19.570" end="00:05:23.314">to closeted public officials<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that we won't be shot down anymore</p>
      <p begin="00:05:23.314" end="00:05:25.212">and obviously all the AIDS issues.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:25.212" end="00:05:27.433">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-I would love to see, like,<br/>more cameras or something </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:27.433" end="00:05:29.192">you know, for our own protection.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:29.192" end="00:05:30.536">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[male voice] and everyone here <br/>has concerns--</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:30.536" end="00:05:32.997">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[Larry] People die everyday.<br/>Friends get sick everyday.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:32.997" end="00:05:35.365">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I don't--it's like being in the trenches.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:35.365" end="00:05:38.933">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There's such anger in the community<br/>and that it's coalescing in a way </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:38.933" end="00:05:41.415">that has never been done before.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:41.415" end="00:05:43.220">- Okay, which way do we face girlfriends?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:43.220" end="00:05:45.102">This way or that way?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:45.102" end="00:05:47.146">[crowd talking]</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49.167" end="00:05:51.128">[cars honking]<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>[crowd cheering and rallying]</p>
      <p begin="00:05:51.128" end="00:05:53.989">[together] HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:54.081" end="00:05:57.693">HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:57.693" end="00:06:01.181">HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:01.181" end="00:06:04.895">HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:04.938" end="00:06:06.912">- [police officer talking]</p>
      <p begin="00:06:06.927" end="00:06:11.352">[crowd shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:06:14.174" end="00:06:16.412">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:06:46.178" end="00:06:49.314">[crowd shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:06:49.413" end="00:06:52.436">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:15.077" end="00:07:18.061">$ How To Survive A Plague. $</p>
      <p begin="00:07:27.245" end="00:07:29.787">- I guess, I'm feeling pretty hopeless<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>at the moment.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:29.787" end="00:07:36.845">I think that the biggest question that<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I'm facing now is how to remain hopeful</p>
      <p begin="00:07:36.845" end="00:07:39.768">in the face of increasing loss.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:40.198" end="00:07:42.992">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[David Barr] I don't know,<br/>maybe it sounds really corny </span></p>
      <p begin="00:07:42.992" end="00:07:43.837">but I--</p>
      <p begin="00:07:46.633" end="00:07:50.405">as difficult as the time is for us,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:52.121" end="00:07:59.470">I like being alive. And I love my friends <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and I love my family.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:59.530" end="00:08:04.070"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">I love people around me.</span><br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>- This, I'm gonna die from this.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:04.108" end="00:08:08.684">This isn't gonna be cured for<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>years and years and years and years.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:08.684" end="00:08:10.320">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- Doctor's office?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:10.320" end="00:08:11.878">- [speaking in the phone] <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>Hi, it's Peter Staley.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:11.878" end="00:08:13.820">It's like living in a war.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:13.820" end="00:08:17.393">All around me,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>friends are dropping dead.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:17.517" end="00:08:21.166">And you're scared for your own life<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>all at the same time.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:23.539" end="00:08:27.245">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was diagnosed with AIDS-related complex</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:27.245" end="00:08:30.539">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">while I was working as a bond trader<br/>on Wall Street.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:30.847" end="00:08:32.676">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I had night sweats.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:32.676" end="00:08:37.644">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I began to get dry, patchy, scaly,<br/>itchy skin on my face. </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:37.727" end="00:08:40.208">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And I would get sick constantly.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:40.208" end="00:08:43.221">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Colds would lay me up for weeks.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:43.798" end="00:08:47.524">I started to look around in desperation</p>
      <p begin="00:08:48.178" end="00:08:56.086">for ways that I could find treatments<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to help save my life.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:58.852" end="00:09:03.830">And there was nothing coming out of our<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>government's efforts, I quickly realized.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:08.705" end="00:09:13.930">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Everything I read said I had about<br/>two years to live, at most. </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:16.082" end="00:09:19.391">[Crowd shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:09:20.129" end="00:09:22.315">$ ACT UPS first protest<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>March 24, 1987 $</p>
      <p begin="00:09:22.315" end="00:09:24.169">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[male voice] WHAT DO WE WANT?</span>
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[crowd answering] A CURE!</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:24.169" end="00:09:26.224">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[male voice] WHEN DO WE WANT IT?</span>
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[crowd answering] NOW!</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:26.224" end="00:09:28.653">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[Peter] I was on my way to work</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:28.663" end="00:09:31.701">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I got handed <br/>a flier about ACT UP and AIDS.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:31.711" end="00:09:35.913">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My mentor says, "If you ask me,<br/>I think they all deserve to die" </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:35.913" end="00:09:37.932">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"because they took it up their butt."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:38.191" end="00:09:43.266">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was deeply closeted and I had to just <br/>stew about it for the rest of the day.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:46.139" end="00:09:48.972">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I got myself to the very next <br/>ACT UP meeting.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:49.085" end="00:09:52.538">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">They could just tap into that<br/>immediate anger and get stuff done.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:52.538" end="00:09:55.106">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[female voice] We need to get approval <br/>on this...</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:55.106" end="00:09:58.608">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This is a non-violent <br/>and quiet kiss-in.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:58.608" end="00:10:01.514">We will not leave until<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>the administrator meets with us</p>
      <p begin="00:10:01.514" end="00:10:06.416">and tells us that Saint Vincent's<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>is willing to make a public statement</p>
      <p begin="00:10:06.416" end="00:10:08.664">condemning gay and lesbian violence.</p>
      <p begin="00:10:08.664" end="00:10:11.630">[crowd cheering and applauding]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:14.666" end="00:10:16.671">- All those in favor?</p>
      <p begin="00:10:18.403" end="00:10:20.515">
