      <p begin="01:14:06.851" end="01:14:08.150">One exception...</p>
      <p begin="01:14:08.150" end="01:14:14.450">- There was one patient that--<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>patient #143, I believe, was his number,</p>
