      <p begin="01:42:52.924" end="01:42:57.430" region="top"> The number of lives saved:<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>6,000,000 $$</p>
      <p begin="01:43:05.654" end="01:43:08.183">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Peter] I'd like to close <br/>with words written</span></p>
      <p begin="01:43:08.183" end="01:43:10.181">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">by fellow AIDS activist, Peter Russo.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:43:10.537" end="01:43:14.691">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">When the future generations ask<br/>what we did in the war, </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:43:14.859" end="01:43:18.829">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We have to be able to tell them<br/>that we were out here fighting. </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:43:19.625" end="01:43:20.928">And we have to leave a legacy</p>
      <p begin="01:43:20.928" end="01:43:24.246">to the generations<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>of people who will come after us.</p>
      <p begin="01:43:24.246" end="01:43:28.855">Remember that someday,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>the AIDS crisis will be over.</p>
      <p begin="01:43:29.560" end="01:43:32.160">And when that day has come and gone,</p>
      <p begin="01:43:32.160" end="01:43:34.506">there will be a people <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>alive on this earth,</p>
      <p begin="01:43:34.506" end="01:43:38.357">gay people and straight people,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>black people and white people,</p>
      <p begin="01:43:38.357" end="01:43:41.899">men and women, who will hear the story,</p>
      <p begin="01:43:41.961" end="01:43:44.918">that once, there was a terrible disease,</p>
      <p begin="01:43:44.918" end="01:43:48.476">and that a brave group of people<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>stood up and fought,</p>
      <p begin="01:43:48.476" end="01:43:52.905">and in some cases died, so that<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>others might live and be free.</p>
      <p begin="01:43:54.628" end="01:43:56.279">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="01:43:56.279" end="01:44:00.654" region="top"> The number of people who die<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>because they can't afford AIDS drugs: $$</p>
      <p begin="01:44:00.654" end="01:44:03.040" region="top"> 2,000,000 every year<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>5,000 every day, 4 every minute $$</p>
      <p begin="01:44:03.040" end="01:44:03.040" region="top"> ACT UP END AIDS. </p>
      <p begin="01:44:12.399" end="01:44:14.764">- [Peter talking]</p>
      <p begin="01:44:37.125" end="01:44:39.448">- Ouch! That hurts!</p>
      <p begin="01:44:46.313" end="01:44:49.413">- Our information is essential<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>so that doctors and patients</p>
      <p begin="01:44:49.413" end="01:44:51.961">can make intelligent treatments.</p>
      <p begin="01:44:54.875" end="01:44:55.974">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Okay. </span><br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>- Alright.</p>
      <p begin="01:44:55.974" end="01:44:57.549">- [male talking]</p>
      <p begin="01:44:57.549" end="01:44:59.868">- No, I won't take that.</p>
      <p begin="01:44:59.868" end="01:45:03.135">- I'm really glad to see everybody here.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>You look really good.</p>
      <p begin="01:45:08.002" end="01:45:10.860">- I'd like to suggest <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that we not be unethical</p>
      <p begin="01:45:10.860" end="01:45:14.410">to do a randomized trial<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>on two different prevention programs.</p>
      <p begin="01:45:16.931" end="01:45:20.736">- If we don't eradicate HIV everywhere<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>we will never eradicate it anywhere.</p>
      <p begin="01:45:26.499" end="01:45:30.596">- We may march without incident<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>or they may arrest us,</p>
      <p begin="01:45:30.596" end="01:45:32.317">but it'll all be fun.</p>
      <p begin="01:45:35.959" end="01:45:40.194">- [male talking]</p>
      <p begin="01:45:43.974" end="01:45:47.011">- We're going to end it today.</p>
      <p begin="01:45:49.199" end="01:45:54.615">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="01:46:06.085" end="01:46:12.653">- In just over two years, that drug<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>went from test tube to full approval.</p>
      <p begin="01:46:15.839" end="01:46:19.786">[applause]</p>
      <p begin="01:46:23.048" end="01:46:27.365">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
